docs {
  # Get Assignment Test Cases (Instructor)

  Returns all test cases (including hidden ones) for the specified assignment.
  The instructor must be assigned to the assignment's course instance.

  ## Endpoint
  GET /api/v1/instructor-assignments/:id/test-cases

  ## Authentication
  Requires Employee, Admin, or Super Admin role.

  ## Response (200 OK)
  ```json
  {
    "assignment_id": "uuid",
    "test_cases": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "description": "Insert and search basic values",
        "input": "insert 5\ninsert 3\nsearch 3",
        "expected_output": "true",
        "is_hidden": false,
        "order_index": 1
      }
    ]
  }
  ```

  ## Error Responses
  - 401 Unauthorized — missing or invalid JWT
  - 403 Forbidden — not assigned to the course instance
  - 404 Not Found — assignment does not exist
}
